<div class="hero-unit">
  <%= image_tag "logo_hero.png", alt: '' %>
  <h1>Save, annotate and share your games</h1>
  <p>Most chess databases are too large and cumbersome to be practical. Create your own microbases and take them with you wherever you go!</p>
  <p>Perfect for storing and annotating your own games. Save small, relevant game collections. Ideal for coaches wanting to share lessons or players doing opening preparation.</p>
  <p>Share and publish your games!</p>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="span6">
    <div class="well" style="height: 120px;">
      <h2>Browse our public microbase</h2>
      <%= link_to 'http://chessmicrobase.com/m/1koly5lq' do %>
        <%= image_tag "binoculars.png", alt: '', class: 'home-browse' %>
      <% end %>
      <p>See our features in this public microbase - no login required.</p>
      <%= link_to "Browse Public Microbase", 'http://chessmicrobase.com/m/1koly5lq', class: 'btn btn-info btn-large' %>
    </div>
    <div class="facebook-widget">
      <iframe src="//www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChessMicroBase&amp;send=false&amp;layout=standard&amp;width=450&amp;show_faces=true&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;font=arial&amp;height=80&amp;appId=239552942808764" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:450px; height:65px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
    </div>
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <br />
    <ul>
      <li>Enter and save your own chess games</li>
      <li>Annotate your chess games</li>
      <li>Engine analysis in your browser!</li>
      <li>Create microbases (small chess databases)</li>
      <li>Add games by copy-paste PGN</li>
      <li>Import games from PGN</li>
      <li>Download games as PGN</li>
      <li>Works on any web-browser or mobile device!</li>
      <li>Publish your chess games on the web</li>
      <li>Embed a PGN viewer on your blog or website</li>
      <li>Easily share a game or entire microbase</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="span6">
    <div class="well" style="height: 120px;">
      <h2>Sign up now for free</h2>
      <%= link_to facebook_sign_in_url do %>
        <%= image_tag "clipboard.png", alt: '', class: 'home-sign-up' %>
      <% end %>
      <p>Start building microbases and adding games.</p>
      <div><%= link_to image_tag('facebook_connect_button.png', alt: 'Connect using Facebook'), facebook_sign_in_url %></div>
      <div>or <%= link_to 'sign up using your email address', new_user_path %></div>
    </div>
    <p style="height: 65px; font-size: 11px; font-style: italic">Free accounts are limited to a maximum of 3 microbases with up to 100
      games each. At any time you can upgrade your account to Premium for
      $19.95/year and store up to 100 microbases with up to 1,000 games in each.</p>
    <h2>You should sign up now if you are...</h2>
    <br />
    <ul>
      <li>A chess coach</li>
      <li>Writing a Chess Blog</li>
      <li>Studying chess</li>
      <li>A tournament chess player (a microbase is better than a
        shoebox for all your old scoresheets!)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>